headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium This Week: The Rune Zhaba
content: Make sure to stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort to enjoy an open bar all week long and then give the Lucky Wheel a spin to walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery prizes and more. This week on the podium is the amphibious Rune Zhaba sitting atop beefy, super-thick tires.
